        "Description": "厄尔尼诺指令 The El Nino Direction\r关卡目标：\r*扮演律师，消灭罗伯多·穆罗\r*扮演律师，用事故消灭莫妮亚·贝里尼\r*扮演律师，用爆炸事故消灭多西亚波萨医生\r*所有制服只能通过镇静注射器进行并完成\r*无尸体被发现\rThe Targets:\r*Eliminate Roberto Mulo when disguise as a lawyer\r*Eliminate Monia Bellini in an accident when you disguise as a lawyer\r*Eliminate Dott.Docciaborsa in an explosion when you disguise as a lawyer\r*All pacifications must be done by sedative syringes\r*No bodies found",
